# Privileged Identity Management (PIM) Lab

## Overview
This project demonstrates how privileged access is managed securely using Microsoft Entra ID PIM.

## Steps Implemented
- Assigned eligible role (User Administrator)
- Configured Just-In-Time (JIT) access
- Activated role temporarily

## Key Concepts
- Privileged Access Management
- Eligible vs Active
- Just-In-Time (JIT)
- Least Privilege
- Identity Security

## Real-World Relevance
PIM reduces security risks by ensuring administrative access is temporary and controlled, minimizing exposure to privileged accounts.
